Privacy Policy
Your Privacy Matters to Us

Introduction
Welcome to DPJhub! This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our platform. By using DPJhub, you agree to the practices outlined in this policy. DPJhub is designed to connect professionals, network, and help businesses grow.

Information We Collect
Personal Information: Name, email address, phone number, job title, company details, etc.
Profile Information: Professional details, resume, skills, and endorsements.
Communication Data: Messages and interactions on the platform.
Technical Data: IP address, browser type, device information, and operating system.
Location Data: General geolocation to offer relevant connections and opportunities.
Cookies and Tracking Data: To enhance user experience, remember preferences, and personalize content.
How We Use Your Information
To create and manage your professional profile.
To connect users with relevant job opportunities, business contacts, and networks.
To enhance and personalize your experience on DPJhub.
To send notifications about job alerts, professional networking opportunities, and messages.
To provide customer support and respond to inquiries.
How We Share Your Information
We do not sell your personal data. However, we may share information with trusted service providers, business partners, and contractors who help us operate and improve the platform. We may also share data to comply with legal obligations, such as responding to subpoenas or protecting the rights of our users.

Data Retention & Security
We retain your data as long as necessary for the purposes outlined in this policy. We take reasonable security measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, alteration, or deletion. These measures include encryption and secure storage.

Your Rights
Access, correct, or update your personal data at any time.
Request the deletion of your account and personal data.
Opt-out of marketing communications and promotional offers.
Request a copy of the data we hold about you.
Contact Us
For any privacy-related concerns, please contact us at support@dpjhub.com or reach us at +91 9990301111.
